**Session**  
[Variable](#/dashboard/nozomi_networks-1b267947-931d-484b-bf52-52981e3c7a72)  

#### Description

This dashboard provides comprehensive insights into network session activity within the Nozomi Networks platform using the Session data stream. 

It displays key metrics for total sessions to monitor real-time network usage. Sessions are broken down by protocol and transport protocol to identify the types of traffic traversing the network. Line charts show trends in transferred bytes and packets over time, helping track bandwidth consumption and detect anomalies. Tables highlight the top 10 source IPs, destination IPs, and VLAN IDs to support threat hunting and network segmentation analysis. A saved search presents essential session attributes including timestamp, session ID, status, zones, protocols, and VLAN ID to assist with investigation and operational monitoring.
